    "This agreement not only vali-dated the questionnaire but also highlighted its effectiveness in capturing the research aims. 5.",
    "Pilot Study: A pilot study designed to ensure the validity and reliability of the questionnaire was conducted as an integral part of the initial data collection process.",
    "The pilot study included 30 participants belonging to the target population and focused on assessing the clarity, relevance, and overall feasibility of the questionnaire.",
    "Feedback from participants indicated that the tool was clear and well-understood, requiring no further modifications.",
